name: Paleta Pals: Sea Salt Sandía
description: A wise man once said, "You can be unhappy before you eat a paleta and you can be unhappy after you eat a paleta, but you're never unhappy WHILE you eat a paleta.” What are paletas, you ask? They are a Mexican frozen treat. Like popsicles, only better, paletas are made with fresh fruit, spices and sometimes creamy ingredients. Paleta Pals are an NFT collectable created by digital artist, Medeebz (@El_Medeebz) and they want be your new BFF (Best Frozen Friend). These delicious designs are meant to remind us that life is like a paleta, so eat it up before it melts!
